  "id": "RAW_07b75653",
  "title": "19 岁华裔少女挑战 Scale AI，AI 数据也能打怪赚钱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247491905&idx=1&sn=f9b502fbe7ce0d3d36afd88cd585b20f",
  "date": "2025-11-20 11:01:00",
  "author": "乌鸦智能说",
  "siteName": "乌鸦智能说",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d634dca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fhc62rY29878fl3enP0kGF6sQEsiadYBAQzwOJsE6Smvarkxh2Gyfic5SA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:unset;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 28px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"padding:8.5px 17px;max-height:none;z-index:auto;background-size:auto;visibility:visible;bottom:auto;clear:none;line-height:29.75px;min-height:0px;border-color:rgb(63, 63, 63);background-position:0% center;float:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;background-repeat:repeat;background-clip:border-box;top:auto;left:auto;border-width:0px;background-image:none;border-style:none;height:auto;min-width:0px;\">\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">AI火了，带火了“买铲子”的数据标注生意。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">Scale AI估值冲到200多亿美元，Surge AI也在谈一轮10亿美元融资。巨头们抢模型，资本们抢数据，只要能产出高质量训练数据，就是“印钞机”。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">就在这样疯狂的背景下，一位19岁的华裔少女Serena Ge，带着一个只有10个人的小团队，拿到了1500万美元</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(63, 63, 63);max-height:none;z-index:auto;background-size:auto;font-size:15px;min-height:0px;float:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;background-repeat:repeat;top:auto;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-image:none;text-align:unset;visibility:visible;bottom:auto;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:none;line-height:29.75px;background-position:0% center;background-clip:border-box;left:auto;widows:1;min-width:0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: #b2b2b2;font-style: italic;\">（约1亿人民币）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve的投资人里除了Chemistry VC、YC，甚至还包括了来自DeepMind、Anthropic、OpenAI的工程师。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">他们看好Datacurve的原因很简单，这家公司做了一件听上去不可思议的事情，把高质量数据标注，做成了一款赏金猎人的游戏。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve搭建了一个叫Shipd的平台，把算法题、调试任务、代码理解、测试用例等中高难度的工程挑战，通通包成一条条“任务关卡”<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: #b2b2b2;font-style: italic;\">（Quests）</span>。价格明码标，工程师通关即可拿钱。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">在短期几个月时间里，就有1.6万名工程师涌入Shipd。成立两个月，Datacurve的收入就突破100万美元，并迅速成为Cohere、Anthropic的数据供应商。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">今天，我们就来说说这家神奇的AI公司。</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 01 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据标注的“赏金猎人”来了</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">今年以来，业内一个越来越明确的共识是：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">限制大模型继续往前走的，不再是算力，而是高质量数据。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在代码、法律、医疗这些高度专业化的领域，“标注”早已不是机械劳动，而变成了一项需要专业知识、结构化能力和推理判断的脑力活。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">数据质量直接决定模型的能力上限，这一点正在被更清晰地看见。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">尤其是能提供高质量数据的创业公司，越来越火了。据彭博社报道，今年7月Surge AI就正在进行一轮10亿美元的融资，估值高达150~250亿美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">他们做的事情很简单，就是雇佣了一大批律师、医生、多语种专家，来做垂直领域的高质量数据标注。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但当行业继续往前看时，一个更难补齐的空白开始显露：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">软件工程的数据需求，几乎没有被满足</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">模型要真正理解编程，不只是理解语法或补全代码，而是要掌握工程师的“思考过程”：为什么这样写？为什么要重构？一次代码审查是怎么判断风险的？一个bug是如何定位的？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这些数据天然稀缺，也极难人工合成，更无法靠大规模外包来生产。它需要真实的工程师、真实的推理和真实的判断。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在这样背景下，Datacurve就出现了。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">作为一家专门提供<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">高质量编程数据</span>的数据标注公司，真正让它与行业里其他数据标注公司区分开来的，是其独特的运作方式。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008228\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d47356a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fhnibr41mnFDGn47aicbeSh5ibpK02rBdtd9Gia8QjAoCrHAaFZ19SiaWnyyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">很多人以为，“数据标注”是低门槛工作。但在AI训练的高端赛道中，这件事对人的要求极高。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">就拿以专业著称的Surge AI来说，它招聘宪法律师的标准，曾在最高法院、美国司法部任职，或顶级律所的前合伙人；医学任务需要能做同行评议、具备临床推理能力的医学研究员；多语言任务则需要全球稀缺的“小语种＋专业背景”人才。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这些人报酬自然不低，往往以承包形式参与，律师的时薪甚至能到500–1000美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">与Surge AI以外包形式找人不同，Datacurve选择了另一条路：把数据标注变成了一场赚赏金的竞赛游戏。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">具体来说，他们打造了一个名为Shipd的平台，并在平台上发布包装好的数据任务，任务覆盖了软件工程的关键环节，包括DSA算法题与题解<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: #b2b2b2;font-style: italic;\">（近似刷题平台LeetCode的题目）</span>、存储库范围代码评估、调试与推理轨迹，以及私有代码库等等。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">为了维持数据质量，Datacurve还设计了一套数据验证流程。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">工程师完成任务后，AI会先进行自动验证；另一批工程师可以接手代码审查类任务，通过发现缺陷获得奖励；最终结果会经过专家复审。只有互审机制无法判断的细节，最终再由人类专家做最后评价。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这种“解题-审错-复查”的闭环，让平台能在规模化分发任务的同时保持质量。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">工程师可以<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">以挑战者的身份自行选择代码任务，每个任务奖励80～100美元不等。干得多，赚得多，不设上限</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">例如，用户@James Shi 上线三天，完成四个任务，任务类型包括性能重构、调试、多语言转换等，已经领取132美元奖励。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008227\" data-ratio=\"0.6783854166666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1994115f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fhIXvADElic46wXLE0CXs5YRr3icEziaBqjyPE8vLooUHzz3NYJhoysPFFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <div data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{&quot;copyFrom&quot;:2066762897},[&quot;p&quot;,{},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;▲&quot;]]]]\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">▲用户@James Shi的个人控制台</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">其官网数据显示，平台已吸引超过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.6万名</span>工程师参与。近期公司披露，平台累计发放的赏金已超过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">100万美元</span>，部分任务的奖励也被推高至250～350美元。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008232\" data-ratio=\"0.8019662921348315\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"712\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b31e600&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fheBfEWXmB1gNb0dBKkb6MY5UYFLQ5S7bYkbXdNqucsFTHeicYYhT0cpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Shipd之所以能迅速吸引工程师，不只是因为“能赚钱”。更关键的是，它营造了一种<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">接近竞技场的氛围</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在这里，工程师的动机不是典型的打工心态，而是挑战、声望和奖励。他们更像在平台中游走的“赏金猎人”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">来自Amazon、AMD、DeepMind、OpenAI、Anthropic、Vercel等公司的从业者，以及算法竞赛选手和CS学生，都在这里做任务、晒成绩、组队和社交。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008226\" data-ratio=\"0.23471698113207548\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c205af0b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fhV7svbicndx16fEzoHDdHYFQu8ZgHCtKluKctpk1EXNYMe5KGr36Jia4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">也正因为有这样的结构化工程数据，Datacurve在成立仅两个月时，收入便突破百万美元，并迅速成为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Cohere、Anthropic</span>等模型公司的数据供应商。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Chemistry VC合伙人Mark Goldberg称它是他“投过增长最快的初创公司之一”，并透露公司在融资期间刚刚签下“史上最大的一笔合同”。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 02 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把数据标注，当成消费产品来做</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">回头看，Datacurve的真正特殊性在于，它找到了一个更轻、也更容易规模化的数据生产方式：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">把数据标注当成一款“面向工程师的消费级产品”来做。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve团队规模不到10人，却能驱动一个超过万名工程师的社区。这种强烈不对称的组织结构，是它与传统外包型数据公司的最大差异：后者依赖线性扩张的人力体系，而Datacurve用的是互联网平台逻辑。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">公司联合创始人Serena Ge把这种方式形容为“<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">让数据生产变成一种消费体验</span>”。许多工程师在Shipd上花的时间，本质上是从游戏、开源社区和刷题练习中迁移过来。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">他们不把自己视为标注者，而是把Shipd当成一个“技能竞技场”——在这里挑战任务、积累声望、赢奖励。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve更像一套<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">能够自我生长的系统</span>：任务拆解、验证、评分和复审被流水线化，大部分质量监控由算法完成，而工程师则在激励机制的驱动下自发承担审核环节。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">平台的边际成本因此极低，扩张速度也不再依赖线性增长的人力，是一种典型的“高倍数平台模型”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">另一个明显的差异是，它重新定义了“贡献者”的角色。在多数数据公司，标注者是外包劳动力；在Datacurve，他们是平台的用户。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">工程师进入Shipd，并不是为了执行琐碎的重复劳动，而是以挑战者身份参与算法、调试、推理等高难度任务。能拿钱确实很重要，不过“解决问题带来的成就感”与“社区声望”是更强的黏性来源。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve成立仅一年就完成种子轮</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:unset;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: #b2b2b2;font-style: italic;\">（270万美元）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">与A轮</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:unset;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: #b2b2b2;font-style: italic;\">（1500万美元）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，总融资1770万美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">虽然规模很小，但是胜在速度。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">投资阵容包括Chemistry VC、YC等知名机构，以及多位来自DeepMind、OpenAI、Anthropic等AI巨头的高管以个人身份参与投资。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008240\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae281ebf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F9VjWVBpa4syfhyIRM88icYTevFlibom2fhS1hQJkXsEooicPOxnAalbqyibJRQUfbcrGV53Ib2osWsW3wWgeLbAeRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-clipboard-cangjie&quot;:&quot;[\\&quot;root\\&quot;,{\\&quot;copyFrom\\&quot;:2066762897},[\\&quot;p\\&quot;,{},[\\&quot;span\\&quot;,{\\&quot;data-type\\&quot;:\\&quot;text\\&quot;},[\\&quot;span\\&quot;,{\\&quot;data-type\\&quot;:\\&quot;leaf\\&quot;},\\&quot;▲\\&quot;]]]]&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">▲</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Datacurve联合创始人，Serena Ge（左）和人Charley Lee（右）</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">投资人看中的不是一个新的数据外包公司，而是一个有机会填补“专家数据缺口”的平台型产品。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve的扩张不依赖人力堆叠，而是更像互联网产品那样具备指数级增长的可能性。它更像是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">一种新型基础设施：一个能够持续吸引高水平专业人士，并将他们的思维过程沉淀为可复用数据资产的系统</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">随着越来越多AI实验室意识到：模型性能的提升，不再取决于算力，而在于是否能持续获得高质量人类推理，这种“平台化的专家网络”显得愈发稀缺。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Datacurve想回答的问题也由此从“如何收集数据”，进一步走向一个更大的命题：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">如果数据变成智能时代重要的生产要素之一，那么工程师社区与数据基础设施能否融合成一套全新的工业系统？</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">文/朗朗</span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "19 岁华裔少女创立 Datacurve，通过\"赏金猎人\"游戏化模式解决大模型高质量编程数据稀缺问题，获 1500 万美元融资。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "19 岁华裔少女创立 Datacurve，通过\"赏金猎人\"游戏化模式解决大模型高质量编程数据稀缺问题，获 1500 万美元融资。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了由 19 岁华裔少女 Serena Ge 创立的 Datacurve 公司及其创新的商业模式。该公司通过搭建名为 Shipd 的平台，将大模型训练所需的高质量软件工程数据标注，转化为\"赏金猎人\"式的游戏化任务。该平台将复杂的算法题、代码调试、推理轨迹等工程挑战包装成\"任务关卡\"，吸引了包括来自 Amazon、DeepMind 等公司的 1.6 万名工程师参与。Datacurve 通过“解题-审错-复查”的闭环机制确保数据质量，并成功摆脱传统外包模式对人力的线性依赖，实现了轻量级、高效率的数据生产。这种将数据标注“消费品化”的模式，使其在成立短时间内实现百万美元营收，并成为 Cohere、Anthropic 等 AI 巨头的数据供应商，获得了包括 Chemistry VC、YC 在内的 1500 万美元融资，展现了其在 AI 数据基础设施领域的巨大潜力。",
